#: applications/luci-app-tor/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/tor/tor-hs.js:86
msgid "Traffic will be forwarded to the target hostname"
msgstr "ການຮັບສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກສົ່ງຕໍ່ໄປຫາຊື່ໂຮສ (hostname) ປາຍທາງ"
